Obviously, he was born a kind soul.

935
00:57:20,947 --> 00:57:24,847
Well, being good doesn't mean
he's not corrupt.

936
00:57:24,848 --> 00:57:26,947
It's very unlikely.

937
00:57:26,947 --> 00:57:28,597
Look at his amygdala.

938
00:57:29,587 --> 00:57:33,307
He's not the type who can sleep
at night after doing something bad.

939
00:57:35,158 --> 00:57:38,938
Okay. I need a new plan
if I'm to get revenge.

940
00:57:39,627 --> 00:57:42,248
Something that suits his altruistic brain.

941
00:57:47,237 --> 00:57:48,688
Ha Ru.

942
00:57:52,607 --> 00:57:54,427
Don't give me that look.

943
00:57:54,677 --> 00:57:56,257
I'm...

944
00:57:57,118 --> 00:57:58,697
struggling already.

945
00:58:07,158 --> 00:58:09,627
(Seobu Police Station)

946
00:58:09,627 --> 00:58:11,838
Gather round, everyone.

947
00:58:12,598 --> 00:58:14,026
I have something to say.

948
00:58:14,027 --> 00:58:16,108
Excuse me.

949
00:58:17,168 --> 00:58:18,818
Go ahead.

950
00:58:19,197 --> 00:58:20,887
As of today...

951
00:58:21,337 --> 00:58:24,257
I resign as the Neuroscientific
Investigation Team's...

952
00:58:25,237 --> 00:58:26,887
consultant.

953
00:58:27,507 --> 00:58:28,977
Find someone else.

954
00:58:28,978 --> 00:58:31,257
Find someone... What?

955
00:58:31,317 --> 00:58:34,628
Can't you at least use your blinkers
before dropping such news?

956
00:58:35,087 --> 00:58:36,617
Is there a reason?

957
00:58:36,618 --> 00:58:38,387
I have no time for this.

958
00:58:38,388 --> 00:58:40,137
You're jobless.

959
00:58:46,868 --> 00:58:48,648
What I mean is,

960
00:58:48,897 --> 00:58:51,878
you're darn busy, and your talent...

961
00:58:52,598 --> 00:58:54,588
Your brain whirs faster,

962
00:58:54,737 --> 00:58:57,077
so you can do lots of things
at the same time.

963
00:58:57,078 --> 00:58:59,078
What's that called? Multi...

964
00:58:59,078 --> 00:59:00,078
Multitasking?

965
00:59:00,078 --> 00:59:02,578
That's it, multitasking. You can do that.

966
00:59:02,578 --> 00:59:06,157
I don't want to exhaust
my brain by multitasking.

967
00:59:06,788 --> 00:59:08,087
I had fun...

968
00:59:08,087 --> 00:59:10,498
solving crimes, and it was rewarding.

969
00:59:11,558 --> 00:59:13,137
Goodbye, all.

970
00:59:14,987 --> 00:59:17,438
- What?
- But...

971
00:59:21,067 --> 00:59:24,098
Go, cling to his leg or something.

972
00:59:24,098 --> 00:59:25,478
Why...

973
00:59:27,538 --> 00:59:28,918
Dr. Brain!

974
00:59:29,978 --> 00:59:33,207
(Seobu Police Station)

975
00:59:33,208 --> 00:59:36,146
Dr. Brain. What's this about?

976
00:59:36,147 --> 00:59:37,998
Is it because of me?

977
00:59:38,018 --> 00:59:39,747
If you get that, stay away.

978
00:59:39,748 --> 00:59:41,168
It is because of me?

979
00:59:41,217 --> 00:59:44,137
Why? What did I do?

980
00:59:44,158 --> 00:59:47,256
Is it because we fought that day?

981
00:59:47,257 --> 00:59:49,108
Okay, I apologize.

982
00:59:49,728 --> 00:59:52,356
What did you do
that you need to apologize?

983
00:59:52,357 --> 00:59:53,967
I challenged you to a fight.

984
00:59:53,967 --> 00:59:55,748
Late at night.

985
00:59:56,168 --> 00:59:58,077
Didn't I make you angry?

986
00:59:58,498 --> 01:00:00,506
You did, yes, that was why.

987
01:00:00,507 --> 01:00:02,217
Still, I'm sorry.

988
01:00:04,308 --> 01:00:05,688
Detective.

989
01:00:14,918 --> 01:00:16,768
(Second Place)

990
01:00:23,857 --> 01:00:25,978
(Second Place)

991
01:00:28,728 --> 01:00:30,148
Detective.

992
01:00:32,638 --> 01:00:34,018
I...

993
01:00:35,208 --> 01:00:37,188
killed someone.

994
01:00:39,038 --> 01:00:40,427
What...

995
01:01:09,337 --> 01:01:11,788
(Brain Works)

996
01:01:11,938 --> 01:01:14,757
I don't get Mr. Heo's motive.

997
01:01:15,547 --> 01:01:18,277
It's oddly discrepant
to the direction of the head wound.

998
01:01:18,277 --> 01:01:19,277
Forget it.

999
01:01:19,277 --> 01:01:21,418
- Action.
- I'll smash your head in!

1000
01:01:21,418 --> 01:01:23,217
No, wait. What was that about?

1001
01:01:23,217 --> 01:01:25,038
Let me be very clear.

1002
01:01:25,158 --> 01:01:27,007
- Gosh.
- This is the last case.

1003
01:01:28,788 --> 01:01:31,057
Is this the real murder weapon?

1004
01:01:31,058 --> 01:01:34,667
I thought of a way
to find the real killer.

1005
01:01:34,668 --> 01:01:36,296
I'll do anything you want.

1006
01:01:36,297 --> 01:01:38,177
I want you to leave.

1007
